rticularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/23692/', '', 'Liraglutide, Lixisenatide', 'Amlodipine, Sacubitril, Aliskiren', 1767369485);
